**Component:** `Data Ingestion & Context Engine`
   - *Description*: Responsible for the extraction, normalization, and temporal alignment of market data. It transforms unstructured signals from external sources (Discord, text reports) and raw CSV bar data into a unified historical context, including session-based price structures and volatility metrics (ATR).
